metadata.name: Neo-Pi ネオ
metadata.description:
“Neo-Pi ネオ” brings out a new version, a new field, the new one to be explored by the artist who speaks to you.

This piece is dedicated exclusively to thank all the buyers who supported me in my last curated drop and is a PFP for use with all rights released being: print reproduction, use for PFP, use for discographies.

4096 X 4096 PNG | Digital Artwork by Yomu Yakadashi 2023
